reviews.text:
Choi Fook may be the same as Choi Fuk.

Choi Fook is located in Olympia Plaza in North Point,  Hong Kong. 

The Dim Sum here is really really good, and they have a great variety. 

They make egg rolls with taro, wonderful shrimp dumpling,  nice Shanghai soup dumplings,  a nice fried roast pork bun.

Get there early if you do not want to be disappointed,  and have to wait 45 minutes to an hour minimum to be seated. 

It is recommended to reserve tables  for dinner at least 2 weeks in advance, because they are usually booked and will turn you away for none available.
Delicious food but not enough staff to provide service.

Attended a wedding there. The wedding is mix of Chinese tradition and modern media-based event. Pro: good food and good service.  Con: everything seemed to be so orchestrated and did not feel natural.  Had to pose for the tea ceremony rather than candid shots.  Unnecessary lighting combinations with lights turned down and spot lights shining into people's eyes.  The MC's presentation was awkward, presenting the couple's private moments without being involved at all with their lives. 

Overall, in terms of facility, very good. In terms of generating atmosphere for the wedding party, not so much.  I wish the bride and groom enjoyed it.

Had dinner on Dec. 31, 2018
Food was good every dish in the picture was perfect. 

but food came out after 1 to 2 hrs. With intervals of 20 to 30 mins. 
Service was good, the manager even personally said sorry for the delay.
Maybe its because of the holiday rush.
Cozy place and nice dim sums ...

result.name: 1881 Heritage (Old Marine Police Headquarters)

reviews.text: Nice to look at. Historical but filled with expensive designer brand stores. Worth a stop to see the old time keeping ball. This used to look out over the harbour.. Not anymore.

Really nice area to buy some of the most luxurious brands around, especially if you like watches! Outdoors area built in an old, classical style of Adobe facades, with escalators around for convenience as well. A real people-draw around TST, with nice cafés on the top floor as well. Not too impressive of a view into any other area, but this place has enough of a great look of its own. Not for every wallet, but if you like luxury this is a recommendation.
The cultural building in Hong Kong, worth a visit!
I went to the area during my bussnis trip for 12 hours but was obe of butiful city, i hope to back again for more time

reviews.text:
彩福喜宴婚宴專門店老闆注意：
居然埋單時比條八婆玩！⋯⋯女職員心理變態絕對有問題，呢個職員一粒老鼠屎害死一個酒樓集團，小心俾人報食環署衛生署！
一家七個人食晚飯賣單$1489....商場$1500可以有兩小時免費泊車，只係要求佢比兩個鐘頭免費泊車，居然條八婆話你唔夠$1500，但係我哋比現金三張$500.
條八婆居然話我哋要食唔夠$1500野喎.我哋同佢講話我哋唔使你找個11蚊啦，我哋當俾貼士⋯（其實都唔使佢找返）⋯佢繼續同我地講話因為唔係打印$1500係打印1489所以唔夠免費停車優惠喎⋯⋯所以要你再嗌多樣嘢喎⋯⋯
咁我最後再同佢講話堅持話我唔需要你找個11蚊啦⋯⋯咁咪$1500囉⋯⋯才死死地氣施捨兩個鐘頭免費停車場俾我哋！但係之前要同佢辯論左成2分鐘！
正常來講人哋唔問...你都會主動問客人有冇泊車，點樣點樣你都係待客之道嚟嘅啫⋯⋯而且酒樓又有呢啲嘅基本服務，居然呢個女人會咁樣做法，你係咪想人哋以後唔幫襯你啊⋯⋯同唱衰你間酒樓集團
到最後呢個八婆一句多謝都冇講....
呢個係一個長頭髮企reception嘅女人，衰格到名我都唔想知佢！雖然你啲食物OK之前服務都OK，但係我哋全家決定以後都唔幫襯呢間酒樓集團！完！

昨晚20/7/2019
